  "description": "This dataset includes genetic maps from four maize biparental crosses\n (A/B, C/B, C/D, and E/F) and marker effects for five traits: grain yield\n (t ha⁻¹ at 150 g H₂O kg⁻¹), grain moisture (g kg⁻¹), test weight (g L⁻¹),\n plant height (cm), and ear height (cm). Marker effects were estimated\n separately for two testers per population. Testers are designated as T1,\n T2, T3, and T4.",
